{"id": "art-484", "label": "Art. 484", "title": "Art. 484: Procedura în faţa instanţei", "slug": "art-484", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_106216139\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1351\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_106216139\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 484:\nProcedura în fa&#355;a instan&#355;ei </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_64097486\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1350\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_64097486\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dac&#259; acordului de recunoa&#351;tere a\nvinov&#259;&#355;iei îi lipse&#351;te vreuna dintre men&#355;iunile\nprev&#259;zute la art. 482 sau dac&#259; nu au fost respectate condi&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la art. 483, instan&#355;a dispune acoperirea omisiunilor în cel\nmult 5 zile &#351;i sesizeaz&#259; în acest sens conduc&#259;torul parchetului\ncare a emis acordul.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_131344841\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1349\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_131344841\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)La termenul fixat se citeaz&#259; inculpatul, celelalte\np&#259;r&#355;i &#351;i persoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259;. Instan&#355;a se\npronun&#355;&#259; asupra acordului de recunoa&#351;tere a vinov&#259;&#355;iei\nprin sentin&#355;&#259;, în &#351;edin&#355;&#259; public&#259;, dup&#259;\nascultarea procurorului, a inculpatului &#351;i avocatului acestuia, precum\n&#351;i, dac&#259; sunt prezente, a celorlalte p&#259;r&#355;i &#351;i a\npersoanei v&#259;t&#259;mate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1193322114\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1348\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1193322114\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dispozi&#355;iile cuprinse în titlul III al\np&#259;r&#355;ii speciale privind judecata care nu sunt contrare\ndispozi&#355;iilor prezentului capitol se aplic&#259; în mod\ncorespunz&#259;tor.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}